{
    "494:0": "gambhīradharmakṣāntiparivartaḥ |",
    "494:1": "tatra bhagavān punarapi candraprabhaṃ kumārabhūtamāmantrayate sma-tasmāttarhi kumāra bodhisattvena mahāsattvenemaṃ samādhimākāṅkṣatā kṣipraṃ cānuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhimabhisaṃboddhukāmena gambhīradharmakṣāntikuśalena bhavitavyam |",
    "494:2": "kathaṃ ca kumāra bodhisattvo mahāsattvo gambhīradharmakṣāntikuśalo bhavati ?",
    "494:3": "iha kumāra bodhisattvena mahāsattvena māyopamāḥ sarvadharmā yathābhūtataḥ prajñātavyāḥ |",
    "494:4": "svapnopamā marīcyupamāḥ pratiśrutkopamāḥ pratibhāsopamā udakacandropamā nirmitopamāḥ pratibimbopamā ākāśopamāḥ sarvadharmāḥ prajñātavyāḥ |",
    "494:5": "yadā ca kumāra bodhisattvena mahāsattvena māyopamāḥ sarvadharmāḥ parijñātā bhavanti,",
    "494:6": "svapnopamā marīcyupamāḥ pratiśrutkopamāḥ pratibhāsopamā udakacandropamā nirmitopamāḥ pratibimbopamā ākāśopamāḥ sarvadharmāḥ parijñātā bhavanti yathābhūtataḥ tadāyaṃ kumāra bodhisattvo mahāsattvo gambhīradharmakṣāntikuśala ityucyate |",
    "494:7": "sa gambhīrayā dharmakṣāntyā samanvāgato rañjanīyeṣu dharmeṣu na rajyate,",
    "494:8": "doṣaṇīyeṣu dharmeṣu na duṣyate,",
    "494:9": "mohanīyeṣu dharmeṣu na muhyate |",
    "494:10": "tat kasya hetoḥ ?",
    "494:11": "tathā hi-sa taṃ dharmaṃ na samanupaśyati,",
    "494:12": "taṃ dharmaṃ nopalabhate |",
    "494:13": "yo rajyeta, yatra vā rajyeta,",
    "494:14": "yena vā rajyeta |",
    "494:15": "yo duṣyeta, yatra vā duṣyeta,",
    "494:16": "yena vā duṣyeta |",
    "494:17": "yo muhyeta, yatra vā muhyeta,",
    "494:18": "yena vā muhyeta |",
    "494:19": "sa taṃ dharmaṃ na samanupaśyati,",
    "494:20": "taṃ dharma nopalabhate |",
    "494:21": "taṃ dharmamasamanupaśyannanupalabhamāno'rakto'duṣṭo'mūḍho'viparyastacittaḥ samāhita ityucyate |",
    "494:22": "niṣprapañcaḥ ...... |",
